    "302208": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Paimon",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Aargh, don't lock us up! Let us out!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Waaah!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "...That's enough, Paimon."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I don't think the guards can hear us anymore."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh yeah, hehe... Paimon got a bit carried away there. How was Paimon's acting just now? Great, huh?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Marvelous."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Not bad, but worse than mine."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hehe, everything's going according to plan so far! We made it into confinement, and Alhaitham's probably done with his part, too."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "That was close."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "We can relax for the time being."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "We even managed to trick Grand Sage Azar. Alhaitham sure knows how to cook up a plan."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "What are we doing next? Paimon has trouble remembering things when she's worked up..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Let's review what we discussed during our strategy meeting."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Right right~! Paimon thinks it went something like this..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Alhaitham",
                    "T": "#...Apart from that, we still have yet another goal in the first stage of our operation, which is to send {NICKNAME} to the confinement room."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#What!? Why do we want to get {NICKNAME} locked up on purpose?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Alhaitham",
                    "T": "#{NICKNAME}'s always been the person the sages are most afraid of, as well as the greatest obstacle to the successful implementation of their plan. They are very aware of the risk {F#she}{M#he} poses to them."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Alhaitham",
                    "T": "#Once {NICKNAME} is imprisoned, the sages will likely think that everything is under control..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Alhaitham",
                    "T": "And with their guard down, the next phase of our plan will have a much higher chance of success."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Cyno",
                    "T": "Hmph, I can already see the pompous looks on their faces."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh, that's a super tricky plan. But, Paimon still thinks it's not really worth it..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Alhaitham",
                    "T": "#That isn't the only reason, of course. {NICKNAME} has a more important task once {M#he}{F#she}'s in confinement."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Alhaitham",
                    "T": "According to the Akademiya scholars in Rahman's custody, Lesser Lord Kusanali has sealed off her consciousness in the Akasha ever since she was captured by The Doctor."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Alhaitham",
                    "T": "That way, they can't pry any more information from her."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Alhaitham",
                    "T": "Even if we break into the Sanctuary of Surasthana, it will take time to awaken Lesser Lord Kusanali's consciousness — we need to do that in advance."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "So our job is to wake up Nahida! Okay, totally worth getting thrown in jail for."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Alhaitham",
                    "T": "The confinement room is inside the Akademiya, close to the Sanctuary of Surasthana. It's a completely enclosed space, and you won't be receiving any visitors."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Alhaitham",
                    "T": "I'll work with Rahman's scholars to make some modifications to your Akasha Terminal. Once you're in, get as close as you can to Lesser Lord Kusanali and try to connect to her consciousness."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Alhaitham",
                    "T": "However, as for whether she'll actually wake up... That will depend on our luck."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh~ No wonder you've been wearing your Akasha Terminal today. It's the one that Alhaitham modified."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Paimon thought they'd take our Akasha Terminals when they locked us up in here. Hmm, were they being careless?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "That wasn't because of carelessness, but of their arrogance."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "They think the Akasha is completely under their control."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Alright, so what now?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "We first need to find the place with the best signal in this room."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Then we try to connect with Nahida."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Sounds easy enough. We can finally talk with Nahida after all this time... Let's do it!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
