    "302211": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Sheikh Zubayr",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Sheikh Zubayr",
                    "T": "Nilou, are you sure about this? You're taking such a great risk for them..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nilou",
                    "T": "I'm sure, and I'm going. You know that I don't like to pass up any opportunity to dance, and this one is especially important."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sheikh Zubayr",
                    "T": "*sigh* Alright. You seem to have a lot of trust in them, so I won't say more on the subject."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sheikh Zubayr",
                    "T": "But if anything happens, the few of us here may not be able to help you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nilou",
                    "T": "Don't worry, they've been through worse. Everything's going to be fine!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sheikh Zubayr",
                    "T": "Alright. You know... if you really do get arrested, we'll do everything we can to get you back. Be careful, even if it's only for our sakes."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nilou",
                    "T": "Hehe, thanks, Mr. Zubayr. You're so very kind."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "302212": {
        "Desc": "Go to the Akademiya",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Hushang",
                    "T": "Nilou! How's it going? Nervous?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nilou",
                    "T": "Definitely more than usual, but it's because I'm worried I won't dance well enough."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Farhad",
                    "T": "It's okay, just focus on your performance. We'll take care of everything else."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hushang",
                    "T": "Heh, you sure know how to talk. Taking all the credit, even though we came here together to help out."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nilou",
                    "T": "Well, thank you both! I'll have to treat you to a meal after all this ends. I really, really appreciate all of your help."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hushang",
                    "T": "Ooh, that sounds great! How can we say no to that?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Farhad",
                    "T": "Alright, let's get back to business. Nilou, we'll be here to keep people from going to the Akademiya, so they don't interrupt your performance."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hushang",
                    "T": "I was planning on telling them something like, \"The Akademiya's been conducting a weird experiment, and some of their test subjects escaped. It's really dangerous there, so stay away!\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "Farhad",
                    "T": "Ugh, you couldn't think of anything better? *sigh* Oh well, I guess it does sound like something the Akademiya would do."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nilou",
                    "T": "Hehe, I think it sounds great. I'm counting on you guys!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hushang",
                    "T": "Don't worry, it'll be a piece of cake!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "302213": {
        "Desc": "Go to the Akademiya",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Vihar",
                    "T": "Hey, Nilou. Sorry, it's great to see you, but I'm really busy right now. Our \"Bait People Away with Yalda Candies\" plan is working beautifully."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Vihar",
                    "T": "Do you want some candy? We have more than we can give out."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nilou",
                    "T": "Vihar, thank you so much for doing all of this, and even dressed up as the Knight of Flowers, no less."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nilou",
                    "T": "I'll pass on the candy, though. I cut back on sweets in the period leading up to a performance, and I'm about to start one!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Vihar",
                    "T": "Haha, you have a point. The \"stage\" is cleared and everything's ready, so you can start your performance at any time."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nilou",
                    "T": "Yeah, thanks to you. I'm really grateful. Alright, time to hit the \"stage\"!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Vihar",
                    "T": "You're welcome. The honor's all mine, since I'll have such a great view of the show."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
