    "302215": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Paimon",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#Ehhh, did you hear that, {NICKNAME}? It sounds like a lot of guards just ran by."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Does this mean the plan has moved onto the next stage?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Certainly sounds like it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "It sounds like Nilou completed her task."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Yep yep! It's great that everything seems to be going well."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Come to think of it, when did Alhaitham replace the Knowledge Capsule that was about to be entered into the Akasha?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "When he pretended that he had been corrupted..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Do you remember when he rushed towards the Grand Sage?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh, so that's when he did it!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Paimon was too nervous to notice."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Speaking of, didn't Alhaitham also yoink the Divine Knowledge Capsule from that mercenary leader in Port Ormos when everyone else was distracted?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "It's a time-tested trick of his..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "He can maintain his composure when things get chaotic."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "That's why he can pull off this kind of thing..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hmph. Why are we complimenting him? Yeah, he's smart and all, but he still makes Paimon's blood boil!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Let's review our plan for this stage again! It's not like we have anything else to do right now anyway, and it'll help us feel more confident."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Paimon remembers that Nilou's task was supposed to go a bit like this..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Alhaitham",
                    "T": "...Now that Lesser Lord Kusanali's consciousness has been forcefully sealed, the core figures of the Akademiya and their guards have started to wear their Akasha Terminals again."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Alhaitham",
                    "T": "With The Doctor's technological support, they think they have nothing to fear."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Cyno",
                    "T": "How despicable of them to rely on such a person."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Alhaitham",
                    "T": "But, this is also our chance."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Alhaitham",
                    "T": "I was originally asked to draft the Knowledge Capsule for the \"Artistic Performances Prohibition Act\" when I was still at the Akademiya."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Alhaitham",
                    "T": "It should be on the Grand Sage's desk right now, and will be entered into the Akasha during the next Jnagarbha Day."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Are they really going to stop all artistic performances? That's horrible..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Alhaitham",
                    "T": "I'll make an identical Knowledge Capsule, but this time, I'll \"smuggle\" some misleading information into it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Alhaitham",
                    "T": "We only need to find an opportunity to switch the capsules. Once it's been entered into the Akasha on Jnagarbha Day, if someone were to be seen performing in public..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Alhaitham",
                    "T": "The sages would definitely use that opportunity to announce the ban, and so the misleading information will be disseminated amongst the guards."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dehya",
                    "T": "Sure sounds complicated, but it seems like if everything goes well, we'll be able to get rid of all the guards in the Akademiya without any effort..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dehya",
                    "T": "That's pretty clever. Gettin' right into their heads."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dehya",
                    "T": "I just have one question. Even if we manage to get the misleading info out to the guards, how can we be sure that they'll believe it?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Alhaitham",
                    "T": "People who are used to relying on the Akasha become less inquisitive, and their ability to distinguish truth from misinformation is significantly reduced... They will view everything the Akasha releases to them as the unequivocal truth."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Cyno",
                    "T": "The Akasha will turn humans into \"machines.\" I've seen it happen many times."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dehya",
                    "T": "Yikes... Good thing I didn't wear it for long when I was working in Sumeru City. At first, I thought it was a good thing, too."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dehya",
                    "T": "By the way, this plan still requires a performer, right?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Alhaitham",
                    "T": "Do you have someone in mind?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dehya",
                    "T": "Nilou of Zubayr Theater. I know her really well. We can trust her."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dehya",
                    "T": "I'm kinda hesitant to ask her to participate in a dangerous plan like this, but we can ask her in person."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Alhaitham",
                    "T": "Alright. After the guards in the Akademiya are gone..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dehya",
                    "T": "Then it'll be time for me and my stowaway brothers to shine."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
