    "302223": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Nahida",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Nahida..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "Should I say \"It's nice to meet you\"?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "This is the first time we've met in real life. Before, we've only met in dreams, consciousness, or when I was in someone else's body."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "We finally meet, Nahida."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "Thank you so much for coming to rescue me, but I also need to apologize..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "During this time, I did some self-reflection. My sense of inferiority and yielding to the Akademiya led to all of this, and created so much trouble for you all."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Don't worry about it. You've also helped us a lot."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "You deserved to be freed."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Exactly! We're here because you're a good archon and one of our friends."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "Hehe... Thanks, you two."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "Whew... Amazing, so this is how it feels to walk out of that cage with my own body."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "It's like I just had an endlessly long dream... I can't even tell if I just woke up or was only now born into this world."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "My concept of \"self\" has become so clear..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "But now doesn't seem to be the time to indulge in this feeling."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "The Akademiya's god creation plan..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Saving Irminsul..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "Um, this is really embarrassing. You all just rescued an archon, and now she needs your help to save her country, and even the entire world."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "It's okay. With you here, Paimon's sure that everything will work out!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "There's one more thing..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "What is it?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "For all the things the Akademiya did to me, and for all the folly it committed in the name of wisdom... As their archon, I will make them pay!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Ah..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Wow! That's the spirit! You're finally standing up for yourself and not letting people walk all over you!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "Hehe... I understand now: To be a better archon, I first need to better myself."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "If you haven't even figured out how to be a caterpillar, how can you be a butterfly?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "This is knowledge that only you yourself could have discovered."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "Yes, true. Hm, that reminds me, I wonder how far along the Akademiya is with their god creation plan..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "We need to hurry and prevent the birth of that false god."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "I need to make some preparations. Since I'm now free, I can establish a direct link to the Akasha and control it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "First things first, I need to remove the restrictions that The Doctor put on me in the Akasha..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "After that, I'll make some adjustments and revoke the sages' permissions. The Akasha will then be like how it originally was: only operable by the archon."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "...After all, the Akademiya betrayed Greater Lord Rukkhadevata's trust."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "This might take some time. In the meantime, you should also work on your own preparations."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "If we don't stop the god creation plan in time, we'll be in for a tough fight."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
