    "302804": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Nahida",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "Looking at its operational status, we must prepare for the worst. The god they wanted to create... is likely close to completion, or already completed."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "That's not a surprise..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I've already seen him control the weather."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh no, what should we do... Paimon can't imagine how hard it would be to fight against a Fatui Harbinger with a Gnosis..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "Are you nervous, Paimon?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "If you really want to know... of course Paimon's nervous! Aren't you too, Nahida?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "Yes, I am. This is probably the first time I'm faced with a calamity of this degree since my birth."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "I feel not just nervous, but curious as well."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Curious...? Curious about what?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "Curious about our fate."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "To me, everything we perceive in this world, everything we learn, and everything that happens to us is considered knowledge."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "And if it's a form of knowledge, then it can be understood."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "However, only fate is about that which has yet to occur, so it has always drawn my curiosity."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "So to me, \"fate\" is the ultimate knowledge."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "That's also why I love observing humans and all the things that happen to them. It all brings me great satisfaction."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "And now, at long last, I'm not just an observer anymore."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "I will personally experience my own fate, with you by my side. Hehe, isn't this such a wonderfully exciting thing?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Ah, so that's what you mean! Paimon thinks she understands what you're feeling."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I'm also looking forward to it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "We won't lose."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "Agreed! Okay, let's continue on. I can sense \"his\" aura from here..."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "302806": {
        "Desc": "Go to where The Balladeer is",
        "Talk": []
    },
    "302807": {
        "Desc": "Talk to The Balladeer",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "This imposing aura... It really feels like a god's..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "A body that capitalizes on The Balladeer's original construction as a mechanical puppet, with the Gnosis serving as a constant power supply..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "How much effort and resources did the sages put into this...?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "From a purely technological perspective, it's a commendable achievement indeed. It's no exaggeration to say this is the culmination of human wisdom."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "You sure are something, dishing out compliments at a time like this..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "But I don't think he's reached the spiritual height of a god."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "So he's still the same, old Balladeer on the inside."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I'm not sure if that's a good or bad thing..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "The Balladeer",
                    "T": "Strife is engraved upon every god and every Gnosis brought forth into this world."
                },
                {
                    "N": "The Balladeer",
                    "T": "Can you feel it? The exhilaration of such power, and the thrill of anticipation for our contention..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Nahida wouldn't feel the same things as you!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "The Balladeer",
                    "T": "Do you not realize... that you are interrupting a conversation between gods? Lowly creature, know your place!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "!!!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Still the same Balladeer we know..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "The strife engraved upon a Gnosis... You're talking about the Archon War."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "Teyvat's current peace was not easily won. I didn't personally participate in the Archon War, but the way I see it..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "All those losses were meaningless, driven by the demands of the \"laws.\" There's no point in bringing it up again."
                },
                {
                    "N": "The Balladeer",
                    "T": "Hehehe, is that so? Yet I am deeply disappointed that I was never allowed the fortuity to personally participate in the Archon War."
                },
                {
                    "N": "The Balladeer",
                    "T": "This is a first — encountering a god in this world who does not crave power."
                },
                {
                    "N": "The Balladeer",
                    "T": "No wonder your own people have abandoned you, God of Wisdom."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "But from now on..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Nahida's followers will only continue to increase in number."
                },
                {
                    "N": "The Balladeer",
                    "T": "Hmph. Your judgment is as your existence: unsubstantial."
                },
                {
                    "N": "The Balladeer",
                    "T": "This is where everything ends, Buer, the God of Wisdom."
                },
                {
                    "N": "The Balladeer",
                    "T": "You should know that wisdom cannot solve every problem. Like now, where your only option is to face me in combat."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "The Balladeer",
                    "T": "Come..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "The Balladeer",
                    "T": "Let us reenact a scene of the Archon War. Come and inaugurate my birth as a god."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
